                                                h3 Essentials
                                                hr
                                                h2 Get Your ID card
                                                p
                                                        | Student ID card is the most imortant thing here in IU plus bus rides here are free with ID cards so try and get it done as soon as possible
                                                        You will be given a time slot in which you have to go to Eigenmann Hall and get the formalities done (hardly takes 10 minutes!).
                                                        Once you have the ID, you can go Sports Recreation Center and get your gym pass.
                                                br
                                                h2 Open a Bank Account
                                                p  
                                                |The bank that is hot favourite among people over here is Chase which is located at 2642 E. 3rd Street. 
                                                You can catch a 9 route bus to reach there which has a stop in front of the bank.
                                                p
                                                | Documents Required to open a checking account:			       
                                                ul
                                                        li Passport
                                                        li Student ID card
                                                        li I-20
                                                        li Univeristy Admission Letter
                                                br
                                                h2 Accomodation 
                                                h4 If you already have a house
                                                p
                                                        | If you have already have an arrangement where to live and have a signed a lease then you should talk to the leasing office just to make sure when you arrive in Bloomington you have your house ready to move in. There have been some cases where people having arrived here found out there house wasn't ready to move in to. Therefore it's very necessary to communicate clearly. 
                                                h4 Haven't found a place to live yet
                                                p
                                                        | If you came to Bloomington and still have to find roommates and sign a lease for a new place then don't panic. Here are some steps that you can follow.
                                                ul
                                                        li Book a room in a lodging near 3rd Street for a night or two, it's reasonable and at a convenient distance from the campus.
                                                        li Talk to some seniors or your incoming classmates if they can help you out with temporary accomodation till you find a place of your own to live. 
                                                        li Visit the housing complexes near the west or the east side of the campus and go and take a look at the different house options pertaining to your needs. 
                                                        li Here are some of the common housing options preferred by international students.
                                                        ul
                                                                li Hoosier Courts
                                                                li Park Doral 
                                                                li Fountain Park 
                                                                li Crescent Park 
                                                                li Smallwood Plaza
                                                                li Ambasssdor Apartments
                                                                li Woodbridge 
