                                                h3 Well! Lets talk about something fun now!
                                                hr
                                                h2 Food in Btown
                                                p
                                                        | If one thing we can be sure about people over here is that they love their food and drinks! Bloomington offers a wide array of food choices that can cater to everyone's food pallette. We've got the amazing milkshakes at Steak n' Shake to amazing fries and burgers at Nick's Hut and Chocolate Moose, you abolutely have got to try the ice cream at Moose! Plus there's a nationwide app that is taking this University town by storm, called Hooked! It hooks you with discounts and offers at a lot of places making food cheap and accessible to student population. Who wouldn't mind saving some bucks on food, right huh ? 
