                                                h2 Beauty of Bloomington 
                                                p
                                                        | Indiana University has been constantly rated as one of the most beautiful university campus throughout States. The open spaces here and surrounding places nearby, the trails, Lakes are breathtakingly beautiful. And, the campus looks like it's just out of a Harry Potter movies. The buildings here looks a lot like Hogwarts. It's truly majestic. The winters here are quite cold but the setting is quite visually stunning. Some of the places to visit while you are here:
                                                ul
                                                        li Lake Monroe
                                                        li Brown County Trails
                                                        li Fairfax State Recreation Center
                                                p
                                                        | Don't forget to check out our Gallery page!
                                                br										  
                                                h2 Orientation and Other Events
                                                p
                                                        | There is a week long or so welcome week for the new students and international students have their own international orientataion which has a lot of cool events being held at different parts of the campus. This is a really cool way of mingling with the crowd and getting to know about the place a bit more. And the best part, there's always free pizza or something! So try and attend these events. 
                                                p
                                                        | The biggest event held for the international students is the BISM's furniture give away for which you have to register yourslef. BISM makes sure students should feel at home here and give away furniture, cutlery, food appliances and deliver it to your doorsteps for free. Yes you read it correct, all of this for free! Wherever you are, whatever you are doing, don't miss this one! 				
